Ealadill <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uforsakenmages.showPublicProfile?language=EN>forsakenmages</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#333333>(7/5/02 7:35:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=392.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Farming for loot or PP</span><hr size=1> solusek A is ok.  i go there on occasion.  fair amount of fine steel drops, and some ore as well.  gnomish miners and xx models drop different sorts of things worth some dough.  also the little plant stuff that is stackable that the goblins drop u would think is worthless actually sells for a fair amount.  just take a few summoned bags for weight reduc to carry all the loot.  u can make more cash faster in other places, but at least hin here there isn't much competition like there is in rathe mountains. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uyomad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>YoMaD</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#333333>(7/5/02 8:16:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=392.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Farming for loot or PP</span><hr size=1> Paineel is the best money. The guards don't cause faction loss, you can sell next to the bank, and they are L. 18-high twenties mobs. They drop a sword and a shield that are worth 7-8pp combined with 104+cha. 19 guards on a 20 min respawn I think. <p><img src="http://212.212.159.196/yomad/imagesP/goodrich2.jpg"></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utearofsoul.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tearofsoul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(7/5/02 8:28:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=392.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Farming for loot or PP</span><hr size=1> Gob Earring.......... Warsilk wood <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
